      "Chunk 03 | chunk accuracy=0.967 | cumulative accuracy=0.922 | memory=103.7 KB\n",
      "Chunk 04 | chunk accuracy=1.000 | cumulative accuracy=0.942 | memory=134.2 KB\n",
      "Chunk 05 | chunk accuracy=0.967 | cumulative accuracy=0.947 | memory=155.8 KB\n",
      "Chunk 06 | chunk accuracy=0.933 | cumulative accuracy=0.944 | memory=181.8 KB\n",
